<html>
<head>
  <meta charset='utf-8'>
  <title>Thank You!</title>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Thanks <%= name %></h1>
  <p>Thanks for coming to our conference. We couldn't have done it without you!</p>

  <p>
    Political activism is at the heart of any democracy and your voice needs to be heard.
    Please consider reaching out to your following representatives:
  </p>

  <table>
  <tr><th>Name</th><th>Websites</th></tr>
    <% legislators.each do |legislator| %>
      <tr>
        <td><%= "#{legislator.first_name} #{legislator.last_name}" %></td>
        <td><%= "#{legislator.website}" %></td>
      </tr>
    <% end %>
  </table>

  <p>
    <% if phone_number == 'INVALID' %>
      <%= "We do not have a valid phone number on record. Please provide your current number if you would like to receive mobile alerts: ___ ___ ____" %>
    <% else %>
      <%= "Our records show your phone number is #{phone_number}. Would you like to receive mobile alerts in the future? Yes __, No __" %>
    <% end %>
  </p>
  
</body>
</html>

